## Smoke-test cpptraj analysis: confirm trajectories load and basic numbers come out.
parm system.prmtop
trajin heat.nc
trajin prod.nc

## Wrap molecules back into the central box (handles periodic boundaries)
autoimage

## RMSD of solute heavy atoms vs first frame (excludes hydrogens, waters, ions)
rms first :1-3&!@H= out rmsd_solute.dat

## Radius of gyration of solute
radgyr :1-3 out radgyr.dat

## Trajectory frame count sanity check (also catches truncated/empty .nc)
trajout solute_only.nc netcdf onlyframes 1,last

run
quit
